data.description: Check out this home at 4220 NE 10th Street, Des Moines, IA! It’s a simple 2-bed, 1-bath house in a nice neighborhood. Inside, there’s a living area, a practical kitchen, and two bedrooms. It’s got a big basement for extra space and a backyard. It’s located in a great school district. With all the stores it's located near, convience best describes this home. Want to see it? Contact your realtor! It’s a good pick if you’re buying for the first time or looking for something more straightforward in Des Moines.
